  "steps": [
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――ひだまりストア・倉庫奥――",
      "bg": "images/assets/bg/bg_hidamari_warehouse.png",
      "bgMode": "forceReplace",
      "forceBackgroundReplace": true,
      "clearStorySprites": true
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空、ここにいたのか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……店長。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "休憩中か？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "休憩というか、手入れ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "手入れ？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空の足元には、細長い布袋と、丁寧に畳まれた道具袋が置かれていた。\n店の備品ではなさそうだ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "それ、弓道の道具か？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "うん。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "持ってきてたんだな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "帰りに道場へ寄る予定だったから。\n少し時間が空いたし、弦の確認をしてただけ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "へえ……本格的だな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "普通。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "普通ではない気がするけど。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "弓を引くなら、手入れくらいするでしょ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空、弓道やってるんだったな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "一応。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "一応で済む腕じゃないって聞いたけど。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "誰から。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "美空から。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……美空、余計なことを。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "日本一って聞いた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "すごいな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "言わなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "褒められるの、苦手だったな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "苦手というか、変な感じがする。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "変な感じ？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "ぼくは、ただ続けてきただけだから。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "続けてきたのがすごいんじゃないか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "そういう言い方、ずるい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ずるいか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "うん。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空は布で弓道具を拭く。\nその手つきは静かで、迷いがなかった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "慣れてるな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "ずっとやってるから。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "どのくらい？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "小さい頃から。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "美空の剣道と同じ頃か？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……たぶん。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "二人とも武道系なんだな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空は剣道。\nぼくは弓道。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "対になってる感じがする。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "あ、今のも余計だったか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "少し。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "悪い。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "謝らなくていい。\nただ、対って言われると……少し引っかかる。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "どうして？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空が剣道だから、ぼくは弓道。\n美空が前に出るなら、ぼくは後ろから狙う。\n美空が声を出すなら、ぼくは黙って構える。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "それも、反対を選んだってことか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……最初は、そうだったのかもしれない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "最初は？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空と同じことをしたら、比べられる。\n同じ場所に立ったら、どっちが上手いとか、どっちが似合うとか、そういう話になる。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "だから、違うものを選んだ。\n美空が竹刀なら、ぼくは弓。\n美空が白なら、ぼくは黒。\n美空が夏なら、ぼくは冬。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "でも。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "続けてるうちに、弓道は嫌いじゃなくなった。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "好きになった？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……嫌いじゃない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "それは、好きに近いやつか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "勝手に翻訳しないで。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "悪い。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "でも……弓を引いてる時は、少しだけ楽。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "楽？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "誰かに話さなくていい。\n笑わなくていい。\n目立たなくていい。\nただ、的を見る。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空らしいな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "また言わない方がよかったか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "うん。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ごめん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "夜空らしいって、何。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "え？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "店長、よく言うでしょ。\n夜空らしいって。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ああ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "それって何。\n美空と違うって意味？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "そういう意味で言ったわけじゃない。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "じゃあ、どういう意味。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "静かだけど、ちゃんと見てるところ。\n無理に前に出ないけど、必要な時はちゃんと動くところ。\n簡単に言葉にしないけど、大事なものは丁寧に扱うところ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "今の道具の手入れも、そう見えた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "それ、今考えたでしょ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "今思ったことを言った。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "だから困る。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "困るのか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "困る。\nそういうのを言われると……逃げ道がなくなる。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "逃げ道？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "ぼくは、美空の反対を選んだだけ。\nそう言ってれば楽だった。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "黒も、冬も、弓道も。\n全部、美空と違う方を選んだだけだって思えば、説明できた。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "でも、今は？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……わからない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "わからない？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "本当にそれだけだったのか。\n反対を選んだだけだったのか。\nそれとも……いつの間にか、ちゃんと自分のものになってたのか。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空自身にも、わからないのか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "うん。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空は、弓道具に視線を落とす。\n指先が、丁寧に紐を整える。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "これを手入れしてる時は、落ち着く。\n的を見てる時も、余計なことを考えなくて済む。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "なら、それは夜空のものなんじゃないか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "簡単に言わないで。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "簡単には思ってない。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "最初の理由が何だったとしても、続けてきたのは夜空だろ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……そうやって、また。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "また？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "見なくていいところを見る。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "見えたから。"
    },
    {
